I click till management button from the operation window
I verify till is available or not if available closed the till
I should see the Open Till Window with title "OPEN TILL"
I click power button1
I'm displaying Open Till window
I press first number of the total
I press second number of the total
I press third number of the total
I press Continue
I verify till is available or not if available closed the till
I press Pay In tab
I enter Paid By as "KamilT"
I enter first number of the payment
I enter second number of the payment
I enter third number of the payment
I click Continue
I should see the Reasons window with title "Reasons"
I select the pay in reason as Paid In
I click OK button to select the payment reason
I press Pay Out tab
I enter Paid To as "KamilT"
I enter first number of the payment
I enter second number of the payment
I enter third number of the payment
I click Continue
I should see the Reasons window with title "Reasons"
I select the pay in reason as Paid Out
I click OK button to select the payment reason
I click Till button
I verify till is available or not if available closed the till
I click the Toggle Icon button
I click POS Icon from Toggle
I closed the order type window
I click All
I click Table Layout tab
I click new check button on the Table layout screen
I select table as "T23"
I select the number of seats as "1"
I tap Continue to finish selecting the number of seats
I click the Settings button
I click POS Icon from Toggle
I close the order type window
I click log off button in order screen
